LoadVMTrack(animator, "Reload", 1234567892, false, Enum.AnimationPriority.Action)
LoadVMTrack(animator, "Shoot",  1234567893, false, Enum.AnimationPriority.Action)


Дальше в функциях:

    EquipAnim() → PlayVM("Equip")
    IdleAnim() → PlayVM("Idle")
    ReloadAnim() → PlayVM("Reload")
    при выстреле → PlayVM("Shoot")



